Package: screenmedR
Type: Package
Title: Filtering Pubmed Articles for a meta-analysis. 
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Theodoros Diakonidis
Maintainer: Theodoros Diakonidis <diakonidis@gmail.com>
Description: screenmedR is a package for automatizing the screening of publications in order to minimize the manual work needed to extract the proper publications for a meta-analysis project.
